// Synthetic 200+function module exercising the cap that
// pre-fix truncated collect_module_func_names at 128 names.
// Functions f1..fN form a chain; rec at the end calls f1 from
// late in the source order (forward reference at scale).
// entry is the consumer-facing surface.

